==English==
[[Category:English nouns]]
===Noun===
'''smith''' (''plural'' '''[[smiths]]''')

#A [[craftsperson]] who works [[metal]] into desired forms using a [[hammer]] and other tools, sometimes heating the metal to make it more [[workable]].

====Related terms====
*[[smithy]] or [[smiddy]]
*[[smithery]]
*[[blacksmith]]
*[[goldsmith]]
*[[gunsmith]]
*[[silversmith]]
*[[swordsmith]]
*[[tinsmith]]
Smith-term can be used to refer to a female vagina [used to go along with another common last name "Johnson" which refers to the male penis]

